<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FdI ERROR: Oops 50x</title>
	<meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">
	<meta name="application-name" content="">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="/error_page/logofdi.ico">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="/error_page/LogoAmbar.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="512x512" href="/error_page/LogoAmbar.png">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="192x192" href="/error_page/LogoAmbar.png">
	<link rel="mask-icon" href="LogoAmbar.svg" color="white">
	<script src="/js/menu.js"></script>
	
    <style>
        @import "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Inconsolata";

        @-webkit-keyframes scan {
            0% {
                background-position: 0 -100vh;
            }

            35%,
            100% {
                background-position: 0 100vh;
            }
        }

        @keyframes scan {
            0% {
                background-position: 0 -100vh;
            }
            35%,
            100% {
                background-position: 0 100vh;
            }
        }

        html {
            min-height: 100%;
        }

        body {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Inconsolata', monospace;
            text-shadow: 0 0 1ex #fad66b, 0 0 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            color: rgba(253, 211, 85, 0.8);
            background-color: black;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#56481d, #30270c), url(/images/noise.gif);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        h1 {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            color: rgba(253, 211, 85, .8);
            text-shadow: 0 0 1px rgba(51, 255, 51, .4), 0 0 2px rgba(255, 255, 255, .8);
        }

        a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        strong {
            color: white;
        }

        a::before {
            content: '[';
        }

        a::after {
            content: ']';
        }

        .noise {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: .02;
            background-image: url(/images/noise.gif);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 1;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0, rgba(0, 0, 0, .3) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%);
            background-size: auto 4px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .overlay::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            display: block;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            animation: scan 7.5s linear 0s infinite;
            background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, left bottom, left top, from(transparent), color-stop(2%, rgba(196, 164, 66, .2)), color-stop(3%, rgba(196, 164, 66, .8)), color-stop(3%, rgba(196, 164, 66, .2)), to(transparent));
            background-image: linear-gradient(0deg, transparent 0%, rgba(196, 164, 66, .2) 2%, rgba(196, 164, 66, .8) 3%, rgba(196, 164, 66, .2) 3%, transparent 100%);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .terminal {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            box-sizing: inherit;
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 4em;
            overflow: auto;
        }

        .terminal div.wrapper {
            max-width: 80ch;
        }

        .output::before {
            content: '> ';
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .terminal {
                padding: 2em;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 568px) {
            .terminal {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                padding: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="noise"></div>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="terminal">
		<img src="/error_page/LogoAmbar.png" width="200" height="200" />
        <h1>Error <span class="errorcode">¡Oops, algo no ha salido bien!</span></h1>
        <p class="output">A veces pasan estas cosas.</p>
        <p class="output">Por favor, prueba a <a id="back" href="/">ir a la página anterior</a> o <a href="/">volver a la inicial</a>.</p>
        <p class="output">Buena suerte.</p>
    </div>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            history.back();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
